{"title":"为庆祝新中国诞生而写","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为庆祝新中国诞生而写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好的河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民作主了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，千真万确，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正改了代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大大换了朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不见工厂的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了我们的代表？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不见乡下老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了我们的代表？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的、欢迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反革命的、打倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友和敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分的很明白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪过与功劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也决不颠倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比是光明岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再蒙灰尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再受强盗侵略！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还要比喻他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他好比自由鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要高飞、高飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向更好的一天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要高飞、高飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着新的国旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着毛主席思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更勇敢，更勤劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要使我们的光景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成呱呱老叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要使我们的命运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成皆大欢笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恭喜呵，恭喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的人民共和国！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}